# Pulse App вЂ“ Project Plan

## Summary
Pulse is a real-time, asymmetric event web app where:
- An **Admin** creates and hosts an event.
- Users join via **automatically generated QR code / room code**.
- Users appear as **dots in a shared lobby**.
- A timed **game loop** displays questions.
- Users vote anonymously.
- Results are visualized live and summarized.

---

## Core Features (MVP)

  ### Admin
- Register / Login (Firebase Auth)
- Create Event (name, theme)
- Auto-generate **unique room code + QR**

#### Admin вЂ“ Question Selection (MVP)
- Browse predefined questions (Firestore)
- Filter by category (e.g. вЂњweddingвЂќ, вЂњtechвЂќ)
- Select questions в†’ add to event question list
- View selected questions in a queue
- Add custom questions to the same list
- Reorder questions (optional MVP+)

- Configure:
  - Question duration
  - Result duration
  - Lobby delay
- Display live lobby (users as dots)
- Start / Pause / Stop game loop
- Control game from:
  - Large screen
  - Mobile (admin panel)

---

### User
- Join via QR / code
- Enter username
- Lobby view (participants as floating dots)
- Receive questions in real-time
- Submit one answer per question (anonymous)
- Confirmation animation on vote
- Return to lobby after answering

---

## Real-time Behavior

- Users join/leave в†’ updates instantly (Firestore listeners)
- When a user votes:
  в†’ A dot appears immediately in selected section (main screen)
- Dots:
  - Anonymous
  - Random position within section
  - One dot = one vote
- Timer synchronized via shared Firestore state
- Game loop runs continuously unless paused

---

## Game Loop Logic

1. Admin starts game
2. Question appears on all devices
3. Timer starts (e.g. 5 minutes)
4. Users vote
   - Votes render live as dots in correct section
5. Timer reaches 0
6. Results screen:
   - % per answer
   - Optional: background dots (users)
7. Result delay (e.g. 5 minutes)
8. Countdown to next question (e.g. 30 seconds)
9. Next question loads automatically
10. Loop repeats

### Admin Controls
- Start game
- Pause / resume game
- Adjust timers live

