### Frontend
- React (Vite)
- React Router
- Zustand (state management)

### Backend (Firebase Only)
- Firebase Firestore (database + real-time)
- Firebase Auth (admin login)
- Firebase Hosting (optional)

### Utilities
- qrcode.react (QR generation)
- nanoid (IDs)

### Styling / UI
- Vanilla CSS

---

## Why Firebase (Key Decision)

- Built-in real-time updates (no WebSocket server needed)
- Simple architecture в†’ faster MVP
- Scales reasonably for early stages
- No backend maintenance

---

