---

## Question System

### Sources
1. Predefined categories (Firestore collection)
2. Admin-created questions

### MVP Behavior
- Load questions by category
- Auto-queue questions sequentially
- No editing during runtime (keeps MVP simple)

---

## Hosting (Free & Simple)

### Frontend + Backend
- Firebase Hosting (recommended all-in-one)

Alternative:
- Vercel (frontend) + Firebase (backend)

---

## Data Privacy

- Anonymous user IDs (nanoid)
- Store only username
- Use localStorage for session persistence
- No sensitive data collected
- Optional privacy notice on join

---

## MVP Scope (Strict)

- Event creation
- QR join
- Lobby with live users (dots)
- Game loop (auto questions)
- Real-time voting visualization
- Results screen (%)
- Admin controls:
  - Start
  - Pause
  - Adjust timers

---

## Nice-to-Have (Post-MVP)

- Avatar builder
- Icebreaker prompts ("Did you know...")
- Topic suggestions
- Sound effects / animations
- Multiple rooms
- Admin preview next question
- Admin change upcoming question during runtime

---

## Risks / Considerations

- Timer sync (use server timestamps from Firebase)
- Prevent duplicate votes (one vote per userId/questionId)
- Handle disconnects (remove inactive users)
- Firestore costs with many users (optimize listeners)

